title: DDFP 272: Debating Matt Ryan, fantasy preview
itunes:title: DDFP 272: Debating Matt Ryan, fantasy preview
description:
Shek welcomes in Handsome Hank and NFL ATL's Chris Wesseling to debate Matt Ryan's NFL quarterback credentials. Then NFL Fantasy Live analyst Michael Fabiano joins to preview which teams will be a fantasy football gold mine in 2014 before a live reaction to Germany's demolition of Brazil in the World Cup semifinals.
